{"tid":2507465,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果香港可以合法持槍，今日橫洲鳳池村居民就唔會畀政府欺壓","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T17:27:33.000Z","uid":270506,"like":37,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b6081be247c0491a89aad1719ce2caf2662d7a46","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:27:48.000Z","msg":"今日橫洲收地嘅事再次證明擁槍權對於保障自由同公義係幾咁重要。美國人之所以自由就係有憲法第二修正案保障人民持槍權利，當暴政出現同欺壓人民嘅時候，人民可以持槍組民兵團抗爭，增加暴政運行成本，令當權者唔可以隨意欺壓人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共咁夠膽欺壓橫洲鳳池村嘅居民，就係因為佢地手無縛雞之力，又唔似鄉黑咁有組織有地下武力，於是港共見到剝削佢地嘅成本相對唔高，就放心壓搾佢地。試諗下如果而家橫洲啲居民好似美國人咁個個攞住枝槍對住啲港共走狗，你估班走狗仲夠唔夠膽咁惡？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmScM6SPUCJ336KxRkrU3TLLgnjFYw1Vphk4MqnkrgDQT9?filename=AmcpWDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmcpWDS.png&h=1fbbc775&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ee0c1c86d0d357006ab95711ed26f2a5c0ea820","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"Oh say can you see~"},{"pid":"52efdcfe9d0b5d4f80e06aa23cd0e46af4b3b9ef","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:36.000Z","msg":"by the dawn's early light"},{"pid":"1bcaf9ddcd0c199ba0e1345a68ff115627aac751","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"What so proudly we hailed"},{"pid":"92603cd540ee1ec1aa79e54a1cf9b1d0a15682a9","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"at the twilight's last gleaming"},{"pid":"2f179c16137a516129faa558cc6ab7657a439f60","tid":2507465,"uid":270506,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight"},{"pid":"81d3e145b453ece3162bce934092b0314fd8199f","tid":2507465,"ui