000Z","msg":"fyi<br />\n<br />\n作地永唔係原居地，且塊地只係當年霸返黎既農地，改建作住宅用途都冇得到政府批准。<br />\n<br />\n香港除了中環聖約翰座堂獲永久地權外，所有土地均是政府擁有。所謂買地、買樓，其實就只是取得政府批租土地的使用權。現時我們普遍稱為業主的，其實只是該土地/份額的租用者，而非真正擁有者。<br />\n<br />\n收回土地條例》(124章)訂明了政府收地的權利及補償的義務。賠償為被收回的土地及其上的任何建築物在收地當日的價值。"},{"pid":"0dc844186d850fbd5e81c05a74001c1d57fd9a30","tid":2507465,"uid":264457,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"睇住你單機真係好好笑"},{"pid":"8eba972f802344d9a31a8515482f5eee1916bd16","tid":2507465,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"槍權比地權更難爭取呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116daaedc0989127c58f70a4d509023c1f395b6b","tid":2507465,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"打死幾個公安咪唔拆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed594a783cc3fb94c35db9347eb738a7648dc809","tid":2507465,"uid":33263,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT5K6EKQ9bGqM4pe3S1zDNTFxNeq3TLimT5oqBHgpCaxr?filename=cBSQSZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBSQSZQ.png&h=db48bd37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbzEQQiETGE1F2Z2WHUrJPQRsT1ymdhVJ96WdBwakLcec?filename=ugCpXrx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugCpXrx.png&h=87932dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR8YJZwf3ZeNteJingLVDZc4YxbYYhjfhBN1PyhTsXTRG?filename=bnV7aMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnV7aMy.jpg&h=bce88964&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSskREJTndS6QDF5UJX4kg15SfmZeFAtwmQ4e58RzFZMT?filename=JTWihrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTWihrz.jpg&h=4d8cfde4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5430bf3d81e4693946046f37697c0f